 Noreena Hertz, author, academic 
and business consultant based at  University College London , 
discusses her new book, "Eyes Wide Open: How to Make Decisions 
in a Confusing World."  Hertz talks with Bloomberg's Kathleen 
Hays and Vonnie Quinn on Bloomberg Radio's "The Hays Advantage."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 17:55
 